2952D865.Line27.83542: It seems to be drawn to the risen remains.

3D110384.Line17.83542: They headed toward Solitude, the top of the hill. The sound of Airidah’s talharpa carried with the wind, and then this madness began.

5A28B2ED.Line1.83542: Airidah came through with a horned woman. Not her normal company, to be sure.

8F5E5EE3.Line25.83542: If your aim is to follow them, you won't get far with all this fog.
